text: Kallista Field (born 7 July 1978) is a New Zealand equestrian. She competed in the individual dressage event at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:New Zealand female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of New Zealand Category:Equestrians at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:People from Pahiatua
